__NOTOC__ 
{{Client function}}
{{Added feature/item|1.5.9|1.5.8|20844|This function indicates if world [[sound]] IDs should be printed in the debug window or not.}}
{{Note|This function only works in development mode.}}

==Syntax== 
<syntaxhighlight lang="lua">bool isShowSoundEnabled ( )</syntaxhighlight>
===Returns===
* Returns ''true'' if world [[sound]] IDs should be printed in the debug window, ''false'' otherwise.

==Example==
You can refer to the example below:
<syntaxhighlight lang="lua">
setDevelopmentMode (true)

addCommandHandler ("devdebug",
    function ()
        showSound (not isShowSoundEnabled())
    end
)
</syntaxhighlight>

==Requirements==
{{Requirements|n/a|1.5.8-9.20844|}}

